The Chronicle Mthabisi Tshuma, Showbiz Correspondent ONLINE comedy sensation Ray Vines known for his Mukukuzvi fame is set to take on former Minister of Energy and Power Development, Fortune Chasi known in the music circles as Chibabest, in a boxing match as part of their comedy charity event. The event dubbed “Mukukuzvi versus Chibabest” will be held on Boxing Day in the capital and will be streamed live on a number of social media pages. World Boxing Federation titleholder Charles Manyuchi is set to officiate the event.